-- France Is in Talks With Qatar Fund on Sale of Areva Stake, Tribune Reports
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-10-07T04:23:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/france-is-in-talks-with-qatar-fund-on-sale-of-areva-stake-la-tribune-says.html
France’s head of state holdings Jean-
Dominique Comolli travelled to Qatar to discuss the possible
purchase of a stake in Areva SA by the country’s sovereign
wealth fund, daily La Tribune reported, without saying how it
got the information.  No accord has yet been reached and the price and governance
questions still have to be decided, the newspaper added.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  